snippet.title: Hidden Cats In Paris
snippet.description:
Meow meow meow mes amies! More than one hundred cats are hidden in the lovely Paris. Start with a Beautiful monochromatic illustration, relax and find all the cats one by one to reveal the final colored art.
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1919550/Hidden_Cats_in_Paris/
